From 1 to 10 my stress level is at about a 6.

00:00:12.440 --> 00:00:15.940
Um my stress level today is probably in-between a 7 and an 8.

00:00:16.260 --> 00:00:18.800
Can I want that please?

00:00:18.800 --> 00:00:20.880
Well my phone was just a stressful situation.

00:00:20.880 --> 00:00:22.760
I dropped it, I lost all my contacts.

00:00:23.400 --> 00:00:28.420
Cause I just came out of court and just trying to relax, trying to get away from all that stress.

00:00:29.140 --> 00:00:31.060
I want to study.

00:00:31.060 --> 00:00:34.920
My recent break up is a little bit of a stress.

00:00:34.920 --> 00:00:36.860
I'm an independent contractor and I work for myself.

00:00:36.860 --> 00:00:39.300
One thing that brings me stress is deadlines.

00:00:39.300 --> 00:00:41.522
It always seems like it is going to fall apart at any second.

00:00:41.522 --> 00:00:44.822
