00:00:44.822 --> 00:00:48.800
The top three things that stress me out is not having enough time..*kid squeals*

00:00:48.800 --> 00:00:51.440
All I want to do is relax.

00:00:52.740 --> 00:00:54.680
I just don't know how.

00:00:55.680 --> 00:00:57.540
*exhale*

00:00:57.880 --> 00:01:00.860
Welcome to this guided meditation.

00:01:03.000 --> 00:01:05.320
Are you ready? Let's begin.

00:01:06.680 --> 00:01:08.680
Find a comfortable position.

00:01:09.680 --> 00:01:12.840
Close your eyes. Take a deep breath in.

00:01:12.840 --> 00:01:13.780
*Inhale*

00:01:13.880 --> 00:01:18.120
And as you exhale, let you body begin to relax.

00:01:18.640 --> 00:01:22.440
Listen to the gentle purry of the happy kitten.

00:01:22.840 --> 00:01:23.580
Purrr

00:01:25.020 --> 00:01:25.860
Purrr

00:01:27.180 --> 00:01:28.580
Purrrrr

00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:32.060
Now open your eyes.

00:01:32.060 --> 00:01:32.860
Meow!

00:01:32.900 --> 00:01:34.460
*Cheerful music starts*

00:02:13.840 --> 00:02:16.000
*Music Pauses* *Dog Wimpers*

